Text.string: Looks like you've activated the ECHOcast streaming service! Your viewers can now enjoy your unfiltered badassery!
I see you've activated your ECHOcasting capabilities! Bravo! May your viewership numbers be mighty!
Ah, doing a bit of ECHOcasting, I see. Excellent! Hello to all your fans from me, Claptrap!
ECHOcasting activated! I'm subscribing to your stream right now!
Welcome to life as an ECHOcaster! Better get shooting and looting! You don't want to keep the fans waiting!
ECHOcast stream is up and running! Go forth and entertain!
You're all set for ECHOcast streaming! Hopefully you don't use it for evil like those Calypso Twins.
Ah, I see you're competing with those Calypso Twins for ECHOcast viewers. Good on ya, Vault Hunter! Show them how it's done.
You found a big fat loot chest! Bravo! As an added bonus: your viewers have a chance at winning a copy of your loot!
Thanks to the magic of ECHOcasting, your viewers have a chance to win a copy of an item of their choice from your loot!
ECHOcasting magic does it again! Hello, viewers! You have a chance to win a copy of any piece of loot you see here!
Loot chest alert! Your luckiest viewers will win a copy of any piece of loot you just found!
Hey, hey! A big old loot chest! Nice! Now, your lucky followers have a chance to win a copy of this loot!
Loot chest event! Hooray! Now your viewers can win a copy of this sweet-ass loot!
Ohhhh, boy! It's challenge time! Are you up for it, recruit?!
Your ECHOcast viewers have initiated a friendly little challenge! Have at it!
It's time for a friendly challenge from your ECHOcast viewers!
Challenge time! Your viewers wanna see if you've got what it takes to be MY number one recruit!
Hey, recruit! Looks like your ECHOcast viewers have a fun little challenge for you!
It's time for a challenge, recruit! You got what it takes?!
Your ECHOcast viewers have issued you a challenge! Get to it!
What's this? Is that the sound of a CHALLENGE I hear on the ECHOnet? It is!
Get ready for a challenge, recruit! Here it comes!
Guess what! It's CHALLENGE TIME!
Ooh! That was a rare spawn! Now your ECHOcast viewers have access to it, too! Miraculous!
You just killed a rare spawn! Now your viewers can do it, too!
Rare spawn taken down! Hey, ECHOcast viewers! You've got access to a new rare spawn mission!
Oh boy, oh boy, oh boy! That was a rare spawn you just took out! Now your viewers can get at it, too!
That was a rare spawn! Now your viewers can take it out, too!
Hey, ECHOcast viewers! Guess what! You now have access to a new rare spawn mission, thanks to the streamer!
Lucky you, ECHOcast viewers! You now have access to a new rare spawn mission, thanks to your plucky streamer!
Your awesome streamer just took down a rare spawn! Now you, lucky viewers, have access to the same one!
Nice! That was a rare spawn! Now your ECHOcast viewers can take 'em down, too!
I deem it to be so: your viewers may now attempt to take out the rare spawn you just killed!
Ooh, some generous viewer threw some cash my way. Anyone else want to get in on this?
Hey, sugars, looks like one of you fine viewers slid some money into my tip jar. Anyone else feeling generous?
Thanks, sugar. I do love a good tip. Anyone else want to help a girl out?
Mighty kind of you, viewer, to throw little ol' me a tip like that. Anyone else care to show me some kindness?
Looks like someone gave me a nice tip. How sweet. Anyone else want to show a girl a good time?
One of you sweet viewers sent me a tip, did you? Much appreciated, sugar. Anyone else want a little appreciation?
Looks like my tip jar is getting a little love. Anyone else want to show me how much you care?
A tip? For me? Aww, thanks. I've always depended on the kindness of viewers. Anyone else feel like passing a little cash my way?
Thanks to a tip from one of you lovely viewers, Moxxi's is open for business. Anyone else want to donate to the cause?
Thanks for the tip. Anyone else want to show my tip jar a little love?
Aw, just so you know, streamer, you have the best viewers.
Let me send a big thanks to all you generous viewers out there.
Well, shucks. All that for little ol' me?
You all are just too sweet, you know that?
Ooh, tip jar's lookin' mighty full. Love it.
I can hardly believe my eyes.
Thank you so much for your support.
You're the real heroes here.
I do love to see that.
Mmm, that's good. Don't stop.
This is gonna be a hell of a drink, thanks to you.
Now to the mixology. Where's my shaker at?
Let's mix up somethin' good, shall we?
I know just what to do. Hang on a sec.
Lemme just mix that up for the streamer.
Back in a jiffy with somethin' spiffy.
Gird your loins, streamer, I got a drink comin' up in a sec.
I'll just give those ingredients a little twist and swirl.
Good choices, viewers. Gimme a sec to mix that up.
One moxxtail, comin' up.
Haven't seen the tip jar so full since I brought on those go-go dancers from Hedon-3.
Oh, my. I do love the sight of a full tip jar. Reminds me of the time Digby Vermouth showed up at karaoke night.
If it were physically possible, I'd send every one of you a thank you card with a signed photo. But I guess you'll have to make do with my undying appreciation.
Well ain't that just a lovely sight. Even more lovely than galaxy-famous ballerina-contortionist Bella Vixenia. And that's a high bar.
I'm just, so touched. I'm blushing more than the time intergalactic man of mystery, Docker Haim, told me I was the most beautiful woman in the six galaxies.
Frankly, this is even better than the night I spent with the top-of-the-line stimu-bots of the Ambrosial Shore on Eros sixty... eight? No. Nine.
You are so, so kind... You know what? I'm gonna tell all my most attractive friends about your generosity.
My cups overfloweth. Oh, and thanks for the tips.
I always do accept affection in the form of monetary currency. Thanks, sugars.
Tip jar's full already? Now I can finally buy Claptrap that birthday present he always wanted. Just kidding. Momma needs a new purse.
Oh, dear me. It appears there is a badass viewer in your midst. Better take it out, Vault Hunter!
I say, Vault Hunter! A terrible badass viewer has appeared in your area! Better slay it!
A terrible beast of a badass viewer has shown their ugly face! Take them down!
Ah, watch yourself, Vault Hunter! There is a new badass viewer in your area!
Badass viewer, ho! And by that I mean, there is a new one near you! Give it a good kicking!
It's time to slay a mighty badass viewer of a... well, a badass. That's the technical term, Vault Hunter.
An invader! A badass viewer invader, no less. Better take them out before they take you out!
A thrilling hunt! A badass viewer hunt! Go on, then! Give your quarry a thorough beating!
Success! Bravo!
Well struck, Vault Hunter!
A thrilling victory!
You are victorious, Vault Hunter!
Badass, my fanny! Well done!
Well done, indeed!
You took down the badass! I'm impressed!
An impressive showing, Vault Hunter!
Ha! You took them down!
Take that, you so-called badass!
Well, that was... less than impressive.
Perhaps next time, Vault Hunter.
There, there, Vault Hunter. We can't win them all.
It would appear they are, indeed, a badass.
The badass wins this round. That's too bad.
And I had such high hopes for that battle.
It's okay, Vault Hunter. You did your best.
Well, at least you tried.
You'll get them next time, I'm sure!
Ah, defeat... that's a shame.
I am reading a CoV weapons cache in your area. Relaying relevant data to your ECHOcast viewers now.
Intriguing. There is a CoV weapons cache near you. I am relaying its location data to your viewers.
It would appear there is a CoV weapons cache nearby. Your ECHOcast viewers will have more information for you.
Ah! A CoV weapons cache has just appeared in your area. I am sending more information to your ECHOcast viewers.
Better pay attention to those ECHOcast viewers! They will be able to point you toward a CoV weapons cache nearby.
I am getting word of a CoV weapons cache in your general proximity. Your ECHOcast viewers will know more.
There is a high-value target nearby. Your viewers will know how to find it.
Vault Hunter, there is a target nearby that I'd like you to kill. Transmitting more information to your ECHOcast viewers.
There is a target nearby that requires a good murdering. Your viewers should know how to find it.
It would appear there is a target nearby that needs to be disposed of. Your viewers will know more.
There is a new target in your vicinity! Ask your viewers for help in finding it.
Excuse me, Vault Hunter? There is a target near you that requires your murderous skills. Your viewers should know how to find it.
There is something nearby that requires your destructive capabilities. Your viewers will know more.
There is a thing for you to destroy, Vault Hunter! Your viewers will be able to tell you how to find it.
It is time to smash a thing. You do like smashing, I assume? Ask your viewers for help in finding it.
Your viewers should be able to tell you where to find a thing that you must destroy. Get to it!
Hello, hello! I'm seeing something nearby that you should destroy. Transmitting more information to your viewers.
Would you like to destroy something? Of course you would. Ask your viewers for help in finding that “something”.
It looks like your viewers have a little present for you. Lucky you.
Hey, sugar. Your viewers sent you a little drink. Bottom's up.
Mixed you up a little somethin' on behalf of your ECHOcast viewers. Enjoy.
Looks like your lovely viewers sent you a drink. How kind of them.
Enjoy some of the finest mixological gifts from your ECHOcast viewers.
Ooh, look at that. A drink from your viewers. Better drink it down.
That drink there should give you a little extra vim and vigor. Not that you needed any more.
Better enjoy that nice cold drink before it gets warm, sugar.
Got a little drink here for you on behalf of your ECHOcast viewers.
Sending a little present your way thanks to your lovely ECHOcast viewers.
The benefits of streaming! Haven't you always wanted to smash something that sounds like me?
What goodies might this little package hold? Better smash it like that follow button and find out!
With many thanks to your ECHOcast viewers, go ahead and crack this bad boy open, Vault Hunter! And say hello to the goodies!
Crack... me... open! And be sure to thank your ECHOcast viewers!
Don't worry, you can't hurt me! Even if you wanted to! Get smashing! And hey, thanks, viewers!
I'm not sure how to say this... pin-ah-ta? Pin-ee-ah-ta? Pinyata? Yeah, that sounds right!
Look at me! Look at me! LOOK AT ME! Your viewers want you to smash me good!
Hey! Over here, recruit! Wanna go all smashy-smashy on this cutie-pie goodie-bag your viewers sent you?
Goodies! Goodies for YOU, recruit! SO LUCKY! THANKS, VIEWERS!
Hey! Hey, over here! Take a look at this! Then SMASH IT on behalf of your ECHOcast viewers!
